    nursingActions: ["Assess dyspnea using patient self-report as the gold standard", "Position patient upright or in position of comfort to ease breathing", "Direct a fan toward the patient's face for comfort", "Administer prescribed opioids and benzodiazepines promptly", "Educate family that appropriate opioid doses for dyspnea do NOT hasten death"],
